{"tid":1613340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日yoho元氣班手足我屌晒你哋老母！","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:23:00.000Z","uid":48119,"like":115,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"e6220492f3cfe3167b372dc52fc7d146111e5932","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"今日搞元朗yohoo元氣個時，有好多手足係咁撚啲員工。<br />\n我事後入元氣問翻，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俾你地撚個幾個員工全部手足黎架！</span></span><br />\n大家注意唔好屌錯人，佢地唔係狗，好多自己人，係屌就屌返啲元氣好啦。<br />\n我地搞元氣，除左搞到佢冇生意，仲係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要connect 入邊啲食客一齊杯美心啊！！</span></span>和理非活動，PR 要做足！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"648942c72f4f2da616460f4e6f03635d0c56f207","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"Push(1/10)"},{"pid":"38b824b644a0985fe2462c5d87bf31bf20e0bb39","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"Push(2/10)"},{"pid":"2100913bf91277876bdd5d6950e079a101d764ff","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"Push(3/10)"},{"pid":"f84fd083f9e25d1a76b609293a699edbd080df5c","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"Push(5/10)"},{"pid":"52fcc2189eeeb5921a3c34b4e8c1220f35d9e0f7","tid":1613340,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23e7af269b97af3ceb8d4b00268c035c26115c1c","tid":1613340,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"Push(6/10)"},{"pid":"7f29380803cad5fdb3542b356ef70c18b0eb18c5","tid":1613340,"uid":4151,"like":3,"dislike":37,"score":-34,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"係手足就唔會介意被撚啦"},{"pid":"1633d136e75cb1a63cdc5eb64034117a6